    "This study focuses on developing an NLP system to identify symptoms of digestive diseases, optimizing the CDS process.",
    "Named Entity Recognition (NER) is utilized to determine tokens associated with disease symptoms.",
    "Through training the model with 50 epochs, an F1-score accuracy of 0.79 is achieved.",
    "Experimental results demonstrate that NER, supported by stemming and stopwords removal in pre-processing, enhances system accuracy.",
